程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim

类 FileAttribute

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.FileAttribute
public class FileAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
Stores related information regarding to a gridsim.datagrid.File entity.
从以下版本开始:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0

  • 构造器详细资料

    • FileAttribute

      public FileAttribute​(java.lang.String fileName, int fileSize) throws ParameterException
      Creates a new FileAttribute object.
      参数:
      fileName - file name
      fileSize - size of this file (in bytes)
      抛出:
      ParameterException - This happens when one of the following scenarios occur:
      • the file name is empty or null
      • the file size is zero or negative numbers
